About
Not your usual observation deck, SUMMIT One Vanderbilt offers three levels of multi-sensory immersive experiences. Here, you can enjoy panoramic views, marvel at mirrored rooms and art installations.
Duration: 1-2 hours

Touristy but fun and entertaining - worth it
Nov 2024 Family
Touristy but fun and entertaining. If you are looking for something to do in NYC, this will fill the void nicely. When we arrived in the morning with our 10:30 tickets, we were greeted by a long TSA-like line. Several greeters checked us in and directed us to the end of the line. The wait to go up the elevator was long - maybe 30 minutes. It wasn't bad though, if you like people watching. They keep you moving on your "journey." The views are fantastic. The various room experiences keep you entertained.
